OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FITV News Central Political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Alison Mackenzie speaks
OL,8,Fwith James and Lee Coates - the sons
OL,9,Fof Ian Coates who was stabbed to death
OL,10,Fby Valdo Calocane - after they gave
OL,11,Fevidence to the official inquiry into
OL,12,Fthe attacks in central London.
OL,14,FThe son of a school caretaker, Ian
OL,15,FCoates, who was stabbed to death by
OL,16,FValdo Calocane in Nottingham, has told
OL,17,Fan inquiry he found out his father had
OL,18,Fdied through an Instagram message from
OL,19,Fa family friend.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FJames Coates, whose 65-year-old father
OL,7,Fwas stabbed just over an hour after 19-
OL,8,Fyear-old undergraduates Barnaby Webber
OL,9,Fand Grace O'Malley-Kumar were killed
OL,10,Fin the early hours of June 13 2023,
OL,11,Fsaid he thought the message was a hoax
OL,12,Fwhen he first read it.
OL,14,FIan Coates' two sons, James and Lee,
OL,15,Fgave evidence on Tuesday 24 March at
OL,16,Fthe official inquiry into the
OL,17,FNottingham attacks, taking place in
OL,18,Fcentral London.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FJames said he had been aware of a
OL,7,Fpolice incident in the city which had
OL,8,Fcordoned off roads as colleagues were
OL,9,Fstruggling to get to work, and later
OL,10,Fthat someone had been killed on
OL,11,FMagdala Road, which was close to where
OL,12,Fhe lived, but had no idea it was his
OL,13,Ffather.
OL,15,F"It wasn't until 3pm that I was
OL,16,Fwalking up the road to my house that I
OL,17,Fdecided to check Instagram. I'd not
OL,18,Fgot notifications on, but I got a
OL,19,Fmessage from (a family friend) saying
OL,20,F'I can't believe what's happened to
OL,21,Fyour dad, please ring me'.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,F"And my first instinct is it's a hoax
OL,7,Fmessage and it's been hacked and
OL,8,Ftrying to get me to ring this number
OL,9,Fand then I asked her is this a joke
OL,10,Fand she messaged again reiterating
OL,11,Fthat I should call her.
OL,13,F"She was in hysterics, she said my dad
OL,14,Fhad been involved in an RTA but she
OL,15,Fhad seen what was going off in
OL,16,FNottingham. I still didn't believe it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
