OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FEarlier today (Tuesday 24 March), Ian
OL,7,FCoates' partner, Elaine Newton, told
OL,8,Fthe public inquiry into the Nottingham
OL,9,Fattacks that she was first told by
OL,10,Fpolice that Mr Coates had died in a
OL,11,Froad traffic accident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FJames told the inquiry they only
OL,7,Freceived a call from Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice 10 minutes before former chief
OL,9,Fconstable Kate Meynell did a press
OL,10,Fconference to let Nottingham residents
OL,11,Fknow what had happened, by which point
OL,12,Fthey had tried calling a helpline they
OL,13,Fsaw on the television, non-emergency
OL,14,Fnumber 101 and even 999 to try to get
OL,15,Finformation about what had happened to
OL,16,Ftheir father.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,F"By then, we'd pieced almost
OL,7,Feverything together ourselves from
OL,8,Fsocial media and the news so then it
OL,9,Fwas just a case of them apologising
OL,10,Fthat we had to do that," he said.
OL,12,FJames's brother Lee Coates told the
OL,13,Finquiry he found Ms Meynell's claims
OL,14,Fon TV that officers were "doing
OL,15,Feverything for the bereaved families"
OL,16,Frude and disingenuous.
OL,18,FHe said: "She'd personally not made
OL,19,Fany contact with us. We'd had to fight
OL,20,Fto find out information about our dad."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]vD@ZOUwD@eO]zD@JOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FJames told the inquiry: "Police logs
OL,7,Fshowed my number was available to
OL,8,Fpolice at 12 minutes to eight in the
OL,9,Fmorning and we didn't get a call back
OL,10,Funtil around 5pm, (which) is
OL,11,Fdisgusting for me."
OL,13,FThe brothers said they felt "abandoned
OL,14,Fand overwhelmed", that they were not
OL,15,Ffully informed about what had happened
OL,16,Fto their father and that they were an
OL,17,F"afterthought" when vigils were
OL,18,Farranged in the city.
OL,26,@nD@YOUsD@SO]uD@]OUvD@PO]yD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FSpeaking of the moment he saw Calocane
OL,7,Ffor the first time in court, James
OL,8,Ftold the hearing: "It struck me how
OL,9,Flarge he was... my dad was six months
OL,10,Ffrom retirement, he was quite skinny,
OL,11,Fhe lived off coffee and cigarettes.
OL,13,F"Seeing his build, I knew there was
OL,14,Fnever going to be any chance of them
OL,15,Fprotecting themselves against him."
OL,17,FIt was at Calocane's sentencing
OL,18,Fhearing that they learned the "full
OL,19,Fextent" of their father's injuries.
OL,26,@pD@SOUuD@AOUwD@cO]zD@_OU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FLee said he was "absolutely
OL,7,Fdistraught" when he heard in November
OL,8,F2023 that he should expect Calocane to
OL,9,Fplead not guilty to murdering his
OL,10,Ffather.
OL,12,F"I promised (Ian's partner Elaine
OL,13,FNewton) that this guy will go away for
OL,14,Fthe rest of her life," he told the
OL,15,Finquiry.
OL,17,F"So when we got this information that
OL,18,Fhe's potentially not going to go away
OL,19,Ffor the crimes that he's committed,
OL,20,Fwhere they're telling you that he's
OL,21,Funsafe to go into a normal prison...
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@KO]tD@AOUvD@VO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,F"Of course, he is, he's a monster, you
OL,7,Fknow, look at what he's done. This is
OL,8,Fwhy we have prisons, no? So we can put
OL,9,Fpeople like this away."
OL,11,FIan Coates' son, James, tells the
OL,12,Finquiry into the Nottingham attacks
OL,13,Fthat he's been diagnosed with PTSD
OL,14,Ffollowing his father's death.
OL,16,FIn a statement he read to the hearing,
OL,17,FJames said that new information he had
OL,18,Ffound out since the inquiry had
OL,19,Fstarted had "astounded" him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]{D@MOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FHe said: "Over the last two-and-a-half
OL,7,Fyears, I thought I'd heard it all,
OL,8,Ffrom missed opportunities, misconduct,
OL,9,Fclinical mistakes and institutional
OL,10,Flaziness but unfortunately, more
OL,11,Frevelations are coming out each week."
OL,13,FHe said: "My innocent father isn't
OL,14,Fhere to see justice and it's a hard
OL,15,Fpill to swallow knowing his attacker
OL,16,Fwon't spend any time behind bars.
OL,18,F"I feel sorry for the people of
OL,19,FNottingham who put their trust into
OL,20,Fthe police, the NHS... who have
OL,21,Fcontinued to fail them."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@fO]uD@JOUzD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Lee told the inquiry he has
OL,7,Fhad to come to terms with the fact
OL,8,Fthat the deaths of his father, Ms
OL,9,FO'Malley-Kumar and Mr Webber were
OL,10,Fpreventable.
OL,12,F"What I have heard at the inquiry so
OL,13,Ffar has left me with many questions,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"It has taken a further toll on my
OL,17,Fmental health and I've been shocked
OL,18,Fand dissatisfied with the responses
OL,19,Fthe witnesses have provided and the
OL,20,Fstances they have fiercely maintained."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@eO]xD@AOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774555873
OL,3,CSon of man stabbed to death in attacks
OL,4,Cfound out about his death on Instagram
OL,6,FHe said: "The people of Nottingham
OL,7,Fdeserve far more than the agencies we
OL,8,Fhave heard from so far. I have not
OL,9,Fbeen reassured by much of the evidence
OL,10,FI have heard."
OL,12,FHis statement concluded: "I stand here
OL,13,Ftoday to fight for my dad. His life
OL,14,Fmattered. He deserved better than what
OL,15,Fhappened to him and I will not stop
OL,16,Fsaying that until it is acknowledged,
OL,17,Fnot just in words but in meaningful
OL,18,Fchange."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@NO]tD@ZOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/15
